      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:37:1",
      "text": [
        "ا عَرَضْنَا كِتَابَ الْفَرَائِضِ عَنْ أَمِيرِ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) عَلَى أَبِي الْحَسَنِ الرِّضَا ( عليه السلام ) فَقَالَ هُوَ صَحِيحٌ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Fazal and Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, both together said, ",
          "‘We presented a book of the Obligations, from Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> to Abu Al-Hassan Al-Reza<sup>asws</sup>, so he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘It is correct’."
        ]
      }
